OL,3,CWorld famous Great Wave goes on
OL,4,Cdisplay in north for first time
OL,6,FOne of the world's most iconic works
OL,7,Fof art is going on display in its
OL,8,Ffirst exhibition in the north of
OL,9,FEngland.
OL,11,FKatsushika Hokusai's Great Wave Off
OL,12,FKanagawa has cult status, adorning
OL,13,Fmany a mug and souvenir tea towel over
OL,14,Fthe decades.
OL,16,FNow the 200-year-old print is on
OL,17,Fdisplay at York Art Gallery, as it
OL,18,Farrives on loan from Maidstone Museum
OL,19,Fin Kent.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
