PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772294630
OL,3,CWorld famous Great Wave goes on
OL,4,Cdisplay in north for first time
OL,6,FThe piece will be one of several by
OL,7,Fthe celebrated Japanese artist forming
OL,8,Fpart of an exhibition of woodblock
OL,9,Fprints from, or inspired by, the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FCurator Eleanor Jackson said it was a
OL,13,F"privilege" to display the piece, and
OL,14,Fthat the exhibition celebrated
OL,15,F"centuries of creativity".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@KO]wD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772294630
OL,3,CWorld famous Great Wave goes on
OL,4,Cdisplay in north for first time
OL,6,FMs Jackson said: "Making Waves
OL,7,Fshowcases an outstanding selection of
OL,8,FJapanese woodblock prints spanning
OL,9,Fcenturies of creativity and artistry,
OL,10,Falongside other spectacular items. To
OL,11,Fbring them together in this way has
OL,12,Fbeen a privilege and we are so excited
OL,13,Fto unveil the exhibition.
OL,15,F"The support of national and regional
OL,16,Fmuseums as well as contemporary
OL,17,Fartists has been instrumental in
OL,18,Fallowing us to tell the story of this
OL,19,Fgorgeous art form.
OL,26,@nD@ROUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772294630
OL,3,CWorld famous Great Wave goes on
OL,4,Cdisplay in north for first time
OL,6,F"We are grateful to them for lending
OL,7,Ftheir precious works to York Art
OL,8,FGallery for this exhibition."
OL,10,FMultiple impressions of the print
OL,11,Fexist, though displays are rare due to
OL,12,Fthem being printed on fragile paper
OL,13,Fwhich must be kept in storage to
OL,14,Fprevent light damage over time.
OL,16,FWhile a version of the Great Wave was
OL,17,Fpreviously displayed at RHS Harlow
OL,18,FCarr in Harrogate six years ago, the
OL,19,Fexhibition will be the first time one
OL,20,Fof the original impressions has been
OL,21,Fto the north.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
