CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772294630
OL,3,CWorld famous Great Wave goes on
OL,4,Cdisplay in north for first time
OL,6,FTo celebrate its arrival, a Japanese
OL,7,F"zen" garden is also being built in
OL,8,Fthe city's Museum Gardens for the
OL,9,Fspring and summer months.
OL,11,FSteve Williams, garden manager at York
OL,12,FMuseums Trust, said: "We want to
OL,13,Fencourage visitors to continue their
OL,14,Fjourney beyond the four walls of the
OL,15,FGallery, leaving behind the 'floating
OL,16,Fworld', as they connect with what we
OL,17,Fhope will be the meditative quality of
OL,18,Four Japanese garden outside."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@EO]tD@VOUzD@]O]
